name: Build.Attributes
desc: Attributes that describe a Builds resource.

items.name: expired
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates if the build has expired. An expired build is unavailable for testing.

items.name: iconAssetToken
items.desc: The icon of the uploaded build.

items.name: minOsVersion
items.desc: The minimum operating system version needed to test a build.

items.name: processingState
items.desc: The processing state of the build indicating that it is not yet available for testing.

items.name: version
items.desc: The version number of the uploaded build.

items.name: usesNonExemptEncryption
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the build uses non-exempt encryption.

items.name: uploadedDate
items.desc: The date and time the build was uploaded to App Store Connect.

items.name: expirationDate
items.desc: The date and time the build  will auto-expire and no longer be available for testing.
